data.description: Two homes, one incredible opportunity! Appealing for investors and owner occupants alike. Unique to this property is that both units are single family houses, perfect for an extended family member to occupy or to use as a rental property for additional cash flow -- All while you enjoy the privacy and luxury of single family living! Or rent out both units as an investment. One house has 2 bedrooms/1.5 baths and the other house has 1 bedroom/1 bath. Large yard, formal dining rooms, spacious eat-in kitchens and each unit has it's own parking & detached garage! Newer water heaters in both units, recently updated kitchen & bath in Unit 1. Established residential neighborhood in a convenient commuter location. Endless possibilities!
